title: Less Angels Crime v 1.1 Android .APK
description:
Adventures of the devil in the city of sins. 
 Explore a small town full of crime.   Spoil everything that's left clean. 
 The power of a thousand creatures in your hands. 
 Hollywood grin.   Wings of the demon.   A real devil, charming and deadly.   How many souls can you steal?   What are you going to do that would not bore you? 
 These questions you have to find answers. 
 Greed and gluttony.   Rage and laziness.   Envy and pride.   And of course lust. 
 All mortal sins of mankind.   All this you will find in different quests
